irschner |editor-first2=S.J.B |editor-last2=Shum |editor-first3=C.S. |editor-last3=Carr |url=http://swbplus.bsz-bw.de/bsz102865434kap.pdf |location=London |year=2003 |ref=harv}} * {{cite book |last1=Sølvberg |first1=Arne |authorlink1=Arne Sølvberg |first2=David |last2=Kung |title=An Introduction to Information Systems Engineering |publisher=Springer |year=1993 |ref=harv}} * {{cite journal |last=Stolterman |first=E. |title=The Nature of Design Practice and Implications for Interaction Design Research |work=International Journal of Design |volume=2 |p=55-65 |year=2008 |ref=harv}} {{refend}}
